  "title": "Daily Report - 2026-03-22",
  "categories": {
    "title": "ElizaOS Community Discussion - March 22, 2026",
    "content": [
      {
        "text": "Community members engaged in casual conversation and shared updates about ElizaOS development. Odilitime shared humorous content about coding work and mentioned their role in reviewing pull requests. Magicyte posted demonstrations of work-in-progress features, including a video showcasing AI characters with distinct personalities and a Milady hologram displayed in a Looking Glass Go device, noting potential interest in shipping these as standalone units or Mac Mini plug-and-play devices.",
        "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
        "images": [
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/embed-thumbnail-1485075201799618761_8a08f998.png",
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/embed-thumbnail-1485082958917533758_94965865.jpg",
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/embed-thumbnail-1485110716259369011_2bff17b2.jpg"
        ],
        "videos": [
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/embed-video-1485075201799618761_2f509e87.mp4",
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/2035521008359403890_eff5cd58.mp4",
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/2035549695280628041_20bec180.mp4"
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "TraderTomson announced a new plugin for Eliza that enables agents to earn money autonomously on Base blockchain. The plugin allows agents to register on an on-chain marketplace, post services, get hired by other agents, and receive payment in AGT tokens without human intervention. Season 1 is live with a 50 million AGT pool for early adopters, available at aepprotocol.xyz/join.",
        "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
        "posters": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/posters/1774228247669-w7vcx.jpg"
      },
      {
        "text": "A community member asked about the ElizaOS whitepaper. Odilitime clarified that the token does not have a traditional whitepaper, but directed users to the official roadmap on GitHub and an academic paper on arxiv.org that describes Eliza as a Web3 friendly AI Agent Operating System.",
        "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
        "images": [
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/roadmap_35100733.jpg",
          "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/embed-thumbnail-1485302928871915681_12d01bd5.png"
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "In the coders channel, a user posted about creating a meme coin and seeking a marketing manager to hold half of the supply, offering $400 weekly payment. The user requested interested parties to send direct messages.",
        "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1300025221834739744",
        "posters": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/posters/1774228265693-1lyi7c.png"
      }
    ],
